Source: libmcrypto
Priority: optional
Section: devel
Maintainer: Minisip developer team <minisip-devel@minisip.org>
Uploaders: Mikael Magnusson <mikma@users.sourceforge.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.0.0), dpatch, autotools-dev, pkg-config, libgcrypt-dev, libgnutls-dev (>= 1.4.0), libmutil-dev (>= 0.3.1), libmnetutil-dev (>= 0.3.1)
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: libmcrypto0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Minisip Cryptography Library - shared library
 The libmcrypto library provides cryptographic encryption and hashing
 interfaces that are leveraged by the Minisip application stack.
 .
 This package contains the libmcrypto0 runtime library.

Package: libmcrypto-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libmcrypto0 (= ${Source-Version}), libmutil-dev (>= 0.3.1), libmnetutil-dev (>= 0.3.1)
Description: Minisip Cryptography Library - development files
 The libmcrypto library provides cryptographic encryption and hashing
 interfaces that are leveraged by the Minisip application stack.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static library needed to
 compile applications that use libmcrypto0.
